{"title_page": "List of Days of Our Lives cast members", "text_new": "{{Use mdy dates|date=May 2019}}\n{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{pp-vandalism|small=yes}}\n{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Days of Our Lives'' cast members}}\n''[[Days of Our Lives]]'' is a long-running American television [[soap opera]] drama, airing on [[NBC]]. Created by [[Ted Corday|Ted]] and [[Betty Corday]], the series premiered on November 8, 1965.<ref name=\"start date\">{{cite news|title=Cinema|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,901746,00.html|work=[[Time (magazine)|Time]]|accessdate=June 10, 2007 | date=November 5, 1965}}</ref> The longest-running cast member is [[Suzanne Rogers]], who has portrayed [[Maggie Horton]] since August 20, 1973, making her one of the [[List of longest-serving soap opera actors#United States|longest-tenured actors in American soap operas]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Newcomb|first1=Roger|title=Today in Soap Opera History (August 20)|url=http://www.welovesoaps.net/2014/08/today-in-soap-opera-history-august-20.html|website=We Love Soaps|publisher=[[Blogger (service)|Blogger]] ([[Google]])|accessdate=April 14, 2015|date=August 20, 2014}}</ref> Original cast member, [[Frances Reid]], was previously the soap's longest-running cast member, portraying Horton family matriarch, [[Alice Horton]], from 1965 to 2007.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Greenblatt|first1=Leah|title=Frances Reid, ''Days of Our Lives'' matriarch, dies at 95|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2010/02/04/frances-reid-days-of-our-lives-dead|accessdate=February 4, 2010|work=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|agency=[[Time Inc.]]|date=February 4, 2010|location=United States}}</ref> Actresses [[Susan Seaforth Hayes]] and [[Deidre Hall]], who portray [[Julie Olson Williams]] and [[Marlena Evans|Dr. Marlena Evans]], are currently the second and third longest tenured actors on ''Days of Our Lives'', joining in 1968 and 1976, respectively.<ref>{{cite news|title=Susan Seaforth joins regular series|work=San Antonio (TX) Light| date=December 8, 1968}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Newcomb|first1=Roger|title=Today in Soap Opera History (June 21)|url=http://www.welovesoaps.net/2014/06/today-in-soap-opera-history-june-21.html|website=We Love Soaps|publisher=[[Blogger (service)|Blogger]] ([[Google]])|accessdate=April 14, 2015|location=United States|date=June 21, 2014}}</ref> The following list is of cast members who are currently on the show: the main and recurring cast members, or those who are debuting, departing or returning to the series.\n\n==Cast==\n\n=== Main cast ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:50%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Actor\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Character\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Duration\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Kristian Alfonso]]\n| [[Hope Williams Brady]]\n| 1983\u20131987, 1990, 1994\u2013present\n|-\n| [[Gina Von Amberg]] <!-- Do not delete Gina or \"2012\" per talk page consensus -->\n| 1998\u20132001, 2012, 2017\u20132020\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Lamon Archey]]\n| [[Eli Grant]]\n| 2017\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Matthew Ashford]]\n| [[Jack Deveraux]]\n| 1987\u20131993, 2001\u20132007, 2011\u20132012, 2016\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Camila Banus]]\n| [[Gabi Hernandez]]\n| 2010\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Mary Beth Evans]]\n| [[Kayla Brady|Kayla Brady Johnson]]\n| 1986\u20131992, 2006\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Galen Gering]]\n| [[Rafe Hernandez]]\n| 2008\u2013present\n|-\n| Rafe Hernandez 2\n| 2011\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Linsey Godfrey]]\n| [[Sarah Horton]]\n| 2018\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[Deidre Hall]]\n| [[Marlena Evans|Dr. Marlena Evans]]\n| 1976\u20131987, 1991\u20132009, 2011\u2013present\n|-\n| [[Samantha Evans]]\n| 1992, 2008\n|- \n| [[Hattie Adams]]\n| 2004, 2016\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[Stacy Haiduk]]\n| Warden Smith\n| 2010\n|-\n| [[Susan Banks]]\n| 2018\u2013present\n|-\n| [[Kristen