> Actresses [[Susan Seaforth Hayes]] and [[Deidre Hall]], who portray [[Julie Olson Williams]] and [[Marlena Evans|Dr. Marlena Evans]], are currently the second and third longest tenured actors on ''Days of Our Lives'', joining in 1968 and 1976, respectively.<ref>{{cite news|title=Susan Seaforth joins regular series|work=San Antonio (TX) Light| date=December 8, 1968}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Newcomb|first1=Roger|title=Today in Soap Opera History (June 21)|url=http://www.welovesoaps.net/2014/06/today-in-soap-opera-history-june-21.html|website=We Love Soaps|publisher=[[Blogger (service)|Blogger]] ([[Google]])|accessdate=April 14, 2015|location=United States|date=June 21, 2014}}</ref> The following list is of cast members who are currently on the show: the main and recurring cast members, or those who are debuting, departing or returning to the series.\n\n==Cast==\n\n=== Main cast ===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"width:50%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Actor\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Character\n! style=\"width:30%;\"| Duration\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Kristian Alfonso]]\n| [[Hope Williams Brady]]\n| 1983\u20131987, 1990, 1994\u2013present\n|-\n| [[Gina Von Amberg]] <!-- Do not delete Gina or \"2012\" per talk page consensus -->\n| 1998\u20132001, 2012, 2017\u20132020\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Lamon Archey]]\n| [[Eli Grant]]\n| 2017\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Matthew Ashford]]\n| [[Jack Deveraux]]\n| 1987\u20131993, 2001\u20132007, 2011\u20132012, 2016\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Camila Banus]]\n| [[Gabi Hernandez]]\n| 2010\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Mary Beth Evans]]\n| [[Kayla Brady|Kayla Brady Johnson]]\n| 1986\u20131992, 2006\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\" | [[Galen Gering]]\n| [[Rafe Hernandez]]\n| 2008\u2013present\n|-\n| Rafe Hernandez 2\n| 2011\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | [[Linsey Godfrey]]\n| [[Sarah Horton]]\n| 2018\u2013present\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"3\" | [[Deidr