0100530023633/http://www.cookingchanneltv.com/chucks-day-off/index.html Chuck's Day Off at CookingChannel.com]\n\n{{Food Network (Canada) series}}\n\n[[Category:Canadian cooking television series]]\n[[Category:Food Network (Canadian TV channel) series]]\n\n\n{{Canada-tv-prog-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Bearcat", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:duplicate categorization; already in subcat", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chuck%27s_Day_Off"}
